{"tid":1536012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家都係到講清朝債券，咁袁世凱債券呢？同樣違債無還清呢","createTime":"2019-09-03T14:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:02:21.000Z","uid":116471,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"397335de8e7d127e509f12d110fd4e5909247c24","tid":1536012,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"善後大借款是1913年中華民國臨時大總統袁世凱的北洋政府向英、法、德、俄、日五國銀行團的一次大借款，款項高達二千五百萬鎊，年息五厘，分47年償清，以解決政府的國庫空虛問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%96%84%E5%90%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%80%9F%E6%AC%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%2596%2584%25E5%2590%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2580%259F%25E6%25AC%25BE&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vgg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=44deea1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%96%84%E5%90%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%80%9F%E6%AC%BE</a>"},{"pid":"f6f7120801136bf0529cd9b7677b27ff4d3533b4","tid":1536012,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:19:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49f010e6905e76a0b43b80ed24440fee531ccc21","tid":1536012,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:21:16.000Z","msg":"仲有好多"},{"pid":"3396965476acc009e74540e4a33ecd3c480e86ab","tid":1536012,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:27:20.000Z","msg":"咩袁世凱債券，嗰d係中華民國債券，係中華民國還㗎。"},{"pid":"01984756d300f366b58f1f26413ac126d3aab91f","tid":1536012,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:41:11.000Z","msg":"2007年3月，美國美國紐約南區聯邦地區法院判決撤銷案件，中華人民共和國政府不必償還債務。"},{"pid":"9f99e801b2afd7754874454af65b70568411d6de","tid":1536012,"uid":195495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00fbf534f151836f079a1e81396e7fd7f934340","tid":1536012,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3396965476acc009e74540e4a33ecd3c480e86ab","tid":1536012,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:27:20.000Z","msg":"咩袁世凱債券，嗰d係中華民國債券，係中華民國還㗎。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:51:29.000Z","msg":"要區分，因為後來段祺瑞政府發行的債券，國民政府講過唔會還。"},{"pid":"cc22